{"tid":1676812,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"11月17號 公益金新界區百萬行 - 香園圍公路","createTime":"2019-10-26T16:43:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-09T08:17:12.000Z","uid":175589,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c61c462c0756f5b8687fd47cd480eeba09c370e5","tid":1676812,"uid":175589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T16:43:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KQnqK9T.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKQnqK9T.png&h=39d5dbe9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n日期\t : \t2019年11月17日 (星期日)<br />\n \t \t <br />\n \t \t <br />\n路線\t :\t步行路線將由香園圍公路之長山隧道南端入口起步，沿長山隧道至蓮麻坑路交匯處後折返至長山隧道南端出口為終點。<br />\n全程長約7.8公里，步畢全程約需2小時。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cTHqK9G.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcTHqK9G.png&h=dfff46c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n百萬行分為「港島、九龍區百萬行」及「新界區百萬行」兩種；此外，<span style=\"color: blue;\">公益金亦不時在重大基建開幕前額外舉辦的百萬行</span> (from wiki)"},{"pid":"d4cfe3b2b4fb1c024cec301795b8e9ee22fa7f22","tid":1676812,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T16:44:18.000Z","msg":"【黃色經濟】有個傻仔整咗個黃藍商鋪認證平台<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/eqgeNS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/eqgeNS</a><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b4c86e28ba4f37781adc0f552def05b347c861c","tid":1676812,"uid":280867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T16:45:22.000Z","msg":"屌講乜撚嘢五大訴求<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1676770\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1676770</a>"},{"pid":"dfca2c3327e565470196cb0442e335849869dce7","tid":1676812,"uid":216992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T08:17:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}